title: Justice Department opens investigation into Minnesota governor and Minneapolis mayor
description: Federal prosecutors are investigating Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz and Minneapolis Mayor Jacob Frey. In response to the news, Frey said in a social media post: "I will not be intimidated."
